text:
Mr FITZGIBBON
 (Hunter—Chief Government Whip) (16:55):  by leave—I move:


That the following bills be referred to the Federation Chamber for further consideration:


Corporations Amendment (Proxy Voting) 2012;


Tax Laws Amendment (2012 Measures No. 3) 2012;


Income Tax (Seasonal Labour Mobility Program Withholding Tax) 2012;


Tax Laws Amendment (Income Tax Rates) 2012; and


National Health Amendment (Pharmaceutical Benefits Scheme) 2012.


Question agreed to.

